latestPosts.caption:
Fundraiser Jam: HOP With Purpose

 1 vs 1 Hip-Hop Battle event dedicated to uniting the dance community for a meaningful cause. 

This fundraiser brings together some of the most talented dancers and passionate supporters to celebrate the essence of hip-hop culture while contributing to positive change.

✨ Category: 1 vs 1 Hip-Hop Battle
✨ Judges Panel:

Aditya aka Daino ⚔️🥷

Vipul aka ghost ⚔️🥷

Rahul aka Suprexx ⚔️🥷

This event offers dancers a platform to showcase their talent, compete at a high level, and engage with a vibrant community,

 all under the watchful eyes of respected and experienced judges. Beyond the competition, FUNDRAISER JAM is about coming together to make a difference  using art, music, and movement to support a larger cause.

We invite dancers, enthusiasts, and supporters to join us for an unforgettable experience filled with energy, passion, and purpose. Let’s dance, connect, and raise funds for a brighter future.

Support by❤️

@universal.jammm 

Media Partner: @the.hiphopsociety

Clothing Partner: @hiphopclothingindia

Flyer design by the one and only: @slayerinmyveinss
Big shoutout to him ❤️🥷🏾

Let’s move not just for ourselves, but for each other.
Tap in. Show up. Give back.

Venue and entry fees will be announced soon 
Stay tuned 🙏⚔️⚔️💯
